smfDpdMemoryOverflow OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Counter32 MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The number of times that the memory for caching records for DPD overran and records had to be flushed. The number of records to be flushed upon a buffer overflow is an implementation specific decision. " ::= { smfStateGroup 2 }
